<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #d32f2f; /* Red color for critical errors */
      }
      h3 {
        color: #f57c00; /* Orange for error type */
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 1em;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        padding: 8px;
        border-left: 3px solid #d32f2f;
        background-color: #ffebee; /* Light red background */
      }
      .error-meta {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 5px;
      }
      .error-type {
        background-color: #d32f2f;
        color: white;
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .cloudwatch-link {
        background-color: #ff9800;
        color: white;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 12px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .cloudwatch-link:hover {
        background-color: #f57c00;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
      }
      .summary {
        background-color: #fff3e0;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>🚨 Scraping Errors Detected</h2>
    
    <div class="summary">
      <p><strong>Summary:</strong> <b>{{totalErrors}}</b> errors detected across <b>{{affectedSites}}</b> site(s).</p>
      <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Review errors and investigate any persistent issues.</p>
    </div>

    <ul>
      {{#each errors}}
        <li>
          <span class="error-type">{{errorType}}</span>
          <strong>{{site}}</strong>
          <div style="margin: 5px 0;">
            <em>{{description}}</em>
          </div>
          <div class="error-meta">
            URL: <code>{{url}}</code><br>
            Time: {{timestamp}}
          </div>
        </li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px; background-color: #e3f2fd; border-radius: 5px;">
      <h3>📋 Investigation Steps</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Check CloudWatch logs for detailed error information and stack traces</li>
        <li>Visit the affected URLs to manually verify site structure changes</li>
        <li>Update selectors or API endpoints if site structure has changed</li>
        <li>Test fixes in a development environment before deploying</li>
      </ol>
      
      <a href="https://console.aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/home?region=us-east-1#logV2:log-groups" 
         target="_blank" 
         class="cloudwatch-link">
        🔍 View CloudWatch Logs
      </a>
    </div>

    <hr />
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">
      Generated automatically at {{generatedAt}} (America/New_York)
    </p>
  </body>
</html>